<main id="content" class="content"> <header> <h1 class="title">The Silent Jesus</h1>
 <p class="subtitle" role="doc-subtitle">Oct 23, 2016 00:00</p>
</header> <p>
God of Grace,
</p>

 <p>
When Jesus was offered <br></br>
the choice to be used <br></br>
or to be silent,
</p>

 <p>
He chose silence.
</p>

 <p>
May I guard against <br></br>
the temptation to craft <br></br>
an image of Jesus to use <br></br>
for my own political <br></br>
and personal use.
</p>

 <p>
Thy will, not my own, Lord.
</p>

 <p>
 <i>Amen</i>
</p>



